data.description: Seller is motivated! Lots of potential! This property is on the National Historic Register as the original site of Camp Baker which was established in 1855. Located on nearly an acre, this home is just waiting for your finishing touches. 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a bonus room that can be the 4th bedroom or an office. Huge deck off the back and huge bonus/family room. Massive shop with basement for all your projects. Home is being sold as-is.
